<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247254>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 20. Fig. 17, Anthaxia (Anthaxia) magnifica Bílý, 1983, holotype Ƥ (NMPC), dorsal aspect, 9.8 mm; Fig. 18, the same, data labels; Fig. 19, A. (A.) mancatula Abeille, 1900, lectotype 3 (MNHN), dorsal aspect, 5.5 mm; Fig. 20, the same, data labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247254/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247252>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 12. Fig. 10, Anthaxia (Anthaxia) mancatula Abeille, 1900 3 (Iran, Ziaran, DBCR), dorsal aspect, 6.6 mm; Fig. 11, the same ventral aspect; Fig. 12, the same, dorsal aspect of anterior portion of body." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247252/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247253>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 16. Fig. 13, Anthaxia (Anthaxia) mancatula Abeille, 1900 3 (Iran, Ziaran, DBCR), dorsal aspect of specimen without pronotal bands, 7.0 mm; Fig. 14, A. (A.) senicula (Schrank, 1789) 3 (Armenia, Vedi, Khosrov Forest Reserve, DBCR), dorsal aspect, 8.2 mm; Fig. 15, the same, dorsal aspect of anterior portion of body; Fig. 16, the same, ventral aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247253/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247264>
    dc:description "FIGURES 59 – 60. Fig. 59, North Iran (Tehrān prov.), 10 km N Ziaran, 2100 m, locality of Anthaxia (Anthaxia) magnifica Bílý, 1983 (on the foreground the small tree of Salix sp. from which were collected the wood samples with larvae); Fig. 60, West Iran (Lorestan prov.), 25 km SE of Dorud, 5 km SE of Darband, 2400 m, topotypical locality of A. (A.) simandli sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/247264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

